    • asCustomWidget

      CustomWidgetBuilder<T> asCustomWidget(Function<BaseSettings,ConfigWidgetFactory<T>> widgetFactorySupplier)
      Finishes building the property and starts building a custom widget for it. A function must be supplied, which returns a widget factory for your custom widget. The function provides some base information which is configured in the returned custom widget builder. This data is to be used in your custom widget. To finish building the widget, use WidgetBuilder.build() which will return the created property.
      Parameters:
      widgetFactorySupplier - The supplier to construct a widget instance
      Returns:
      The custom widget builder
